<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation - Lum√©ra</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .order-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .order-info h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #212529;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .items-table th,
        .items-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .items-table th {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .items-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .total-row {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .shipping-info {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .shipping-info h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        .support-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .support-section h3 {
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .support-steps {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .support-step {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        .support-step strong {
            color: #f59e0b;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #f59e0b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .info-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .info-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ Order Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your purchase, {{customerName}}!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>We're excited to let you know that your order has been successfully placed and is being processed. Here are the details:</p>

            <!-- Order Information -->
            <div class="order-info">
                <h3>üìã Order Details</h3>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Order Number:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Order Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{orderDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><strong>${{totalAmount}}</strong></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Items Table -->
            <h3>üõçÔ∏è Items Ordered</h3>
            <table class="items-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Item</th>
                        <th>Quantity</th>
                        <th>Price</th>
                        <th>Total</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{name}}</td>
                        <td>{{quantity}}</td>
                        <td>${{price}}</td>
                        <td>${{total}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td colspan="3"><strong>Total</strong></td>
                        <td><strong>${{totalAmount}}</strong></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- Shipping Information -->
            <div class="shipping-info">
                <h3>üöö Shipping Address</h3>
                <p><strong>{{shippingAddress.name}}</strong></p>
                <p>{{shippingAddress.address}}</p>
                <p>{{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}} {{shippingAddress.zipCode}}</p>
                <p>{{shippingAddress.country}}</p>
                <p>üìû {{shippingAddress.phone}}</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Support Section -->
            <div class="support-section">
                <h3>üÜò Need Help? We're Here for You!</h3>
                <p>If you have any questions about your order or need assistance, our support team is ready to help you every step of the way.</p>
                
                <div class="support-steps">
                    <div class="support-step">
                        <strong>Step 1:</strong> Click the "Contact Support" button below to start a chat with our admin team.
                    </div>
                    <div class="support-step">
                        <strong>Step 2:</strong> Provide your order number ({{orderNumber}}) when starting the conversation.
                    </div>
                    <div class="support-step">
                        <strong>Step 3:</strong> Describe your question or concern, and our team will respond promptly.
                    </div>
                    <div class="support-step">
                        <strong>Step 4:</strong> You can also reach us via email at {{companyEmail}} or call {{companyPhone}}.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                    üí¨ Contact Support Now
                </a>

                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d;">
                    <strong>Quick Support Options:</strong><br>
                    üìß Email: {{companyEmail}}<br>
                    üìû Phone: {{companyPhone}}<br>
                    üí¨ Live Chat: Available 24/7
                </p>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d;">
                We'll send you another email when your order ships. Thank you for choosing {{companyName}}!
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>{{companyName}}</strong></p>
            <p>Your premier destination for quality products and exceptional shopping experience.</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>üìß {{companyEmail}}</p>
                <p>üìû {{companyPhone}}</p>
                <p>üåê <a href="{{frontendUrl}}">{{frontendUrl}}</a></p>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
                ¬© 2025 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
